; Coverage test for op.cc O_LOOKUP evaluation path (line 292-304)
; Tests the dot (.) lookup operator which accesses object members.
; Also exercises the O_LOOKUP print path (line 764).

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --display 'parent.total > 0'
24-Jan-01 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
end test
